				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$r_i$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M22"><mml:msub><mml:mi>r</mml:mi><mml:mi>i</mml:mi></mml:msub></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="11229_2016_1268_Article_IEq11.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula> defined as follows:<disp-formula id="Equ2"><label>2</label><alternatives><tex-math id="M23">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
