</p><p id="Par23">It turns out that our results do not vary much with the value of <inline-formula id="IEq86"><alternatives><tex-math id="M181">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
