				\begin{document}$$\alpha $$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M182"><mml:mi mathvariant="italic">&#x003b1;</mml:mi></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="11229_2016_1268_Article_IEq86.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula>. What counts is that the <inline-formula id="IEq87"><alternatives><tex-math id="M183">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
