</p><p>Notice that in the proof of Theorem <xref ref-type="sec" rid="FPar1">1</xref>, the actual value of the likelihood ratio <italic>x</italic> is not relevant. All that matters is whether <inline-formula id="IEq115"><alternatives><tex-math id="M235">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
